### Shared Conventions

- Sandbox base URL: `https://sandbox.cashfree.com`
- Production base URL: `https://api.cashfree.com`
- Always use env vars for `CASHFREE_APP_ID` and `CASHFREE_SECRET_KEY`
- Latest PG API version: `2025-01-01`
